2:T752,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Article Forge better than ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Article Forge scores 4.0 overall while ShortlyAI scores 5.0. Article Forge is best for bulk article generation and PBN content, while ShortlyAI excels for blog posts and long-form articles."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Article Forge or ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Article Forge starts at $27/mo and ShortlyAI starts at $79/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Article Forge to ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Article Forge and ShortlyAI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Article Forge vs ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Article Forge holds an overall rating of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. ShortlyAI has an overall rating of 5/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Article Forge for fully automated one-click article generation and ShortlyAI for clean distraction-free interface."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Article Forge or ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend ShortlyAI for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Article Forge remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize fully automated one-click article generation. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json"