c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Article Forge and ShortlyAI share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form. Where Article Forge pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Seo Tools and Multilingual and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, ShortlyAI uniquely offers Short Form, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Article Forge holds an overall score of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while ShortlyAI scores 5/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Article Forge offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $27/mo, compared to ShortlyAI's starting price of $79/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
