10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Article Forge is best suited for bulk article generation, PBN content, automated blogging, SEO content, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. ShortlyAI, meanwhile, shines for blog posts, long form articles, stories, distraction free writing, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2015, Article Forge describes itself as \"Fully automated AI article generation in one click.\" ShortlyAI, established in 2020, positions itself as \"Distraction-free AI writing tool focused on long-form content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **ShortlyAI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (5.0 vs 4.0). However, this does not mean Article Forge is a poor choice — far from it. Article Forge excels in its own right, particularly for bulk article generation and PBN content.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value clean distraction-free interface, go with ShortlyAI. If fully automated one-click article generation matters more to you, Article Forge is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
